Detailed Description

cvmx_mio_ptp_clock_hi

This register provides bits <95:32> of the PTP clock. Writes to MIO_PTP_CLOCK_HI also clear MIO_PTP_CLOCK_LO. To update all 96 bits, write MIO_PTP_CLOCK_HI followed by MIO_PTP_CLOCK_LO. MIO_PTP_CLOCK_CFG[PTP_EN] needs to be enabled before writing this register.
